category TLCore
depend hyphen-base
depend hyph-utf8
shortdesc Chinese pinyin hyphenation patterns, unaccented.
longdesc Hyphenation patterns for transliterated Mandarin Chinese (pinyin) in T1/EC and UTF-8 encoding, unaccented.
execute AddHyphen \
	name=pinyin \
	lefthyphenmin=1 \
	righthyphenmin=1 \
	file=loadhyph-zh-latn.tex \
	file_patterns=hyph-zh-latn.pat.txt \
	file_exceptions=

